Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.13,0:00:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So that flowers may bloom with innumerable deaths\Nproviding their nourishment,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.29,0:00:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!\NSo that flowers may bloom with innumerable deaths\Nproviding their nourishment,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.54,0:00:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!\Nthere are countless tragedies\Nburied at the bottom of this beautiful world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,there are countless tragedies\Nburied at the bottom of this beautiful world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!\Nthere are countless tragedies\Nburied at the bottom of this beautiful world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.83,0:00:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,there are countless tragedies\Nburied at the bottom of this beautiful world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.92,0:00:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But unless you are one of those directly concerned,\Nthis is not something you can know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You should simply be captivated\Nby the utterly dazzling beauty and push on,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.17,0:00:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on...\NYou should simply be captivated\Nby the utterly dazzling beauty and push on,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.08,0:00:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You should simply be captivated\Nby the utterly dazzling beauty and push on,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko...\NYou should simply be captivated\Nby the utterly dazzling beauty and push on,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.54,0:00:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,treading firmly on the ground below.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me behind, Riko!\Ntreading firmly on the ground below.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.17,0:00:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,For your tragedy, too, is sure to become sustenance\Nand give birth to the blooming of new flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.54,0:00:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.88,0:00:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.13,0:00:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.63,0:00:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.63,0:00:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Her heart is still beating...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.17,0:00:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's likely to stop any moment now, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:00:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.88,0:01:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a fluffy stuffed doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come here to comfort you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who the heck are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.00,0:01:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy to properly introduce myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but first wouldn't it be best to hear\Nabout how to save her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.42,0:01:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.21,0:01:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This's quite bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell me! I want to save Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.79,0:01:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do to get her breathing again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.17,0:01:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just blow a breath directly into her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a kiss, you know, a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's breathing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:01:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't begin to express my gratitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still too early to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.71,0:02:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it seems she's not regaining consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.63,0:02:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-that can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.46,0:02:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You, come on and carry the girl back to my hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.29,0:02:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.13,0:02:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll find a way to do something for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you don't know anything about us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just keep a little distance between us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Cave-raiding equipment...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.79,0:03:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are those... whistles?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,H-hey... who exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.50,0:03:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I suppose I never told you my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nanachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.42,0:03:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm what you cave raiders would call...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.21,0:03:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, unable to resist, goes down in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:04:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Make those eyes shine brighter than a torch
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The destination we are aiming for is deep
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We squarely lose our way
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The trap of the open-mouthed netherworld
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's chase the traces of truth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If an answer can be found now, we don't mind losing it all
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The echo is still reverberating
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So that we do not part with that voice
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The compass is always
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.79,0:04:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Pointed to the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where there is no escape
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,In that direction
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.96,0:04:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that is a curse
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The pulse is the real thing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Never again will the yearning stop
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A "Hollow"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.17,0:05:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A small... child...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.42,0:05:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't know about us, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose you don't exactly look like a cave raider.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, lay her down over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi, I don't mean to be rude,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.75,0:05:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,but aren't you about the same age as us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling anxious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.54,0:05:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, you wanna try finding someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.50,0:05:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.96,0:05:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.42,0:06:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Among cave raiders, handling it like this\Nis apparently common practice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's just because they don't know\Nthe proper way to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.42,0:06:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The poison will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.42,0:06:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, just calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll allow the poison to flow through her body\Nand then get rid of it once it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is medicine made from a friend of mine\Nthat I then hardened with wax.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.79,0:06:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's not possible to administer it orally,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you need to insert it in the butthole...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, on to her arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna remove the smashed bone fragments\Nand stitch up the blood vessels and flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, this white thing is a nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A number of them were damaged...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not good at stitching these, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.71,0:06:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, the way you cut her is pretty gruesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.13,0:06:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a good thing she passed out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I think that should do for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But, now comes the hard part.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to need you to go out\Nand fetch a bunch of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just tell me what I need to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for doubting you earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm begging you, Nanachi! Please save Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,why didn't you cut her at the elbow joint?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You could've taken her arm off from the joint\Nwithout breaking the bone first...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you perhaps just following her directions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.42,0:07:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She's an extraordinary girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yeah...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If the part past the elbow is left intact,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,then it totally changes the things\Nit's possible to do when out cave raiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She was still determined to press on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.71,0:08:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Even finding herself in that situation,\Nshe still didn't give up on her adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.96,0:08:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Riko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, th-that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I still haven't told you our names!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Reg! And that's Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time anyone like you two has come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.88,0:08:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since you entered my hunting grounds,\NI've been listening to everything you've said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the presence I sensed right after\Nwe entered the fourth layer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It was you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was watching the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.79,0:09:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, I wouldn't be able to treat\Nthe orbed-piercer's poison, would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.08,0:09:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, even when that thing attacked us, you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was watching... and I heard it all, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The look on your face says,\N"Then why didn't you help us?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.33,0:09:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I was simply interested in what the deal was\Nwith you guys, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,From the very beginning,\NI had no intention of showing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,S-so then, why did you save us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I started to pity you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Riko, don't leave me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You were sobbing like some lost little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't bear to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there someone else here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.63,0:09:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just somebody I live with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.08,0:09:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my cute little Mitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl is also a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard about the strain\Nof ascending in the sixth layer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quite sure it was,\N"the loss of your humanity or even death."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.50,0:10:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, if someone survives the Curse of the depths'\Nsixth layer, this's what becomes of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Their personality and intellect vanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As the name implies, they become a hollow husk\Nof the person who once was.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what anyone tries,\Nthey can never go back to the way they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.75,0:10:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That trick you used where you extended your arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thinking about what would happen if you did that\Non the sixth layer is pretty thrilling, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.58,0:11:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,B-but, Nanachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.46,0:11:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's a reason, you see,\Nthat I'm an exception among exceptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get your hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.79,0:11:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitty, you're special, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If a cave raider becomes a Hollow,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,their fellow cave raiders will put them to death\Nand collect their belongings before moving on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Given the alternative, I suppose it's far better\Nto simply tell people they died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.58,0:11:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In that environment, imagine putting yourself\Nout in the open looking like I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I am living proof that it's possible to return\Nfrom the sixth layer while retaining your humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.50,0:11:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally, people will come and try to capture me\Nhowever they can, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.58,0:11:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Revealing myself is a big risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it was only out of pity,\Ngetting saved is still a good thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.79,0:11:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's your situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a pushover...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.83,0:12:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm done sketching it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The materials necessary for healing Riko\Nand the places to find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My awesome signature is on there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She still has internal bleeding\Nand her arm will rot off at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, all I've done so far is delay her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.54,0:12:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll manage to hold on for another 12 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.96,0:12:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If it starts seeming like it'll take longer than that,\Nyou better think of a tactful way to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,D-don't joke around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you can't see it then, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Later... I need to ask what that means exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There's so much to keep up with\Nthat my mind is churning...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But, for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:12:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,think only of saving Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.58,0:13:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.00,0:13:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, my eyes didn't deceive me, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.79,0:13:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This new Cartridge is just great.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look happier...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all thanks to you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, smile...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us celebrate the success of the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can gather most of the stuff on the western side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.88,0:13:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay out of the central region. Orby is in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,"Orby"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Nanachi mean the orbed-piercer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A demonfish, the bigger the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.25,0:14:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Choose one that displays clear color differentiation\Nbetween its back and belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.88,0:14:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant-hammerbeak eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Take just one per nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.29,0:14:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The freshly-laid ones are best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.42,0:14:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.75,0:14:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sto-!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.33,0:15:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yellow-shining grass.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.38,0:15:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Find a spot with lots of it growing\Nand pick the stuff that smells somewhat better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.13,0:15:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A shroombear infected with water-shrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I've collected it all now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... Make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-wh-what are you...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.96,0:16:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you sure are noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If we just leave her soaked in bloody pee,\Nshe'll get a rash, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.58,0:16:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She really peed a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.88,0:16:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to wash it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,is Riko alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Also... I misunderstood and... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just calm down, you piece of junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this one's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.96,0:16:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's get started right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to save Riko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.17,0:16:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.46,0:16:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,These water-mushrooms are parasitic, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,When it looks like their host, which has left the den\Nby this point, is about to kick the bucket,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,they share their stored-up nutrients\Nand get their host going again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If the number of shroombears in a new den increases,\Nthere'll be more water-shrooms, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what's known as a symbiotic relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.08,0:17:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,While Riko's still unconscious, we're going to plant them\Non her and put 'em to good use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got a good vein there anyway,\Nso we'll plant 'em right on her wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That should help the bone's healing process a bit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They also help prevent the rotting of the flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.04,0:17:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they do hurt like crazy\Nwhen you pull 'em off, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanachi, what are you going to use the fish\Nand the rest of the stuff for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That should be obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,For my dinner, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I gathered all this!\NWhat would we do if I'd been too late?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you sure get noisy about every little thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this business about being noisy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:17:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,With the state Riko's in...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.63,0:18:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been watching over her this whole time,\Nso it's not like I can go and find food myself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.88,0:18:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If I collapse from hunger, who's going to treat her then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really a pushover...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it doesn't look pretty,\Nbut at least this will save her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Her life is truly saved this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nanachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.50,0:18:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, you're so irritating!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.13,0:18:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are fluffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.96,0:18:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Go wash Riko's pee-stained clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a riverbed out back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.50,0:18:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.42,0:19:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"Flowers of Fortitude"...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternal Fortunes, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Are these...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,gravestones?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be going now, Lyza...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.58,0:19:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,the Blaze Reap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But why is it here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure it was kicked away somewhere\Nby the orbed-piercer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.25,0:19:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Where...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Riko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.08,0:19:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nanachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.75,0:20:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.67,0:20:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This thing... Somewhere or other, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.08,0:20:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Nanachi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.54,0:20:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.71,0:20:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.46,0:20:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You were staring intently at a girl's pee-stained clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,H-huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.38,0:20:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the Blaze Reap's right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So, have you seriously become a piece of junk or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.04,0:20:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you have been through a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.46,0:20:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And while you're at it, wash this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:21:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-what was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it the scenery of somewhere similar?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, that voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that was one of my own...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,my own memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, the one\Nwho was mourning for Lyza was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I bury her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Ozen said, "No one was buried there."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.25,0:21:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it all mean...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.38,0:22:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The glittering waves that float in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.63,0:22:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's bundle them and build a rainbow bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.00,0:22:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A dangerous foothold, a slope we slide on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.13,0:22:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A signpost of the past and future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.54,0:22:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Your left hand, with my right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.38,0:22:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Join it, connect us, and let's begin
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.13,0:22:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am always beside you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.79,0:22:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past, the present, and also the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's walk along without hesitating
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.17,0:23:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Pile up multicolored dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will we head toward tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.75,0:23:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can be together with you, the world will begin to shine
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's search for flowers that bloom at the ends of the earth
